name: CryptoSerpent #023
description: Igor Feral doesn’t remember anything from his past except his name, it’s believed that someone may have caused him a mutation, since that there are more records of mutations strangely similar to Pokémon. His memories begin with an explosion where he escaped from a strange building. After his getaway, he went to live in a small town where the children friendly call him Nessie. He spends the day taking care of them although the little ones cry because his appearance is a bit terrifying.
